-연산자\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B4%80%EA%B3%84-%EC%97%B0%EC%82%B0%EC%9E%90\" aria-label=\"관계 연산자 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>관계 연산자</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>관계 연산자는 두 수의 관계를 비교하여 참(true) 또는 거짓(false)을 결과로 얻는 연산자이다.</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>거짓은 0, 참은 1로 사용되지만 0외의 모든 숫자도 참으로 간주된다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"-1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-1\" aria-label=\" 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h4>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>연산자</th>\n<th>의미</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>==</td>\n<td>같다</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>!=</td>\n<td>같지 않다</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>></td>\n<td>크다</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>>=</td>\n<td>크거나 같다</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&#x3C;</td>\n<td>작다</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&#x3C;=</td>\n<td>작거나 같다</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"비트-연산자\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%B9%84%ED%8A%B8-%EC%97%B0%EC%82%B0%EC%9E%90\" aria-label=\"비트 연산자 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>비트 연산자</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>비트 연산자는 비트별(0, 1)로 연산하여 결과를 얻는 연산자이다.</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<h4 id=\"-2\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-2\" aria-label=\" 2 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h4>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>연산자</th>\n<th>의미</th>\n<th>비고</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>&#x26;</td>\n<td>and</td>\n<td>모든 비트가 1일 때만 1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>^</td>\n<td>xor</td>\n<td>모든 비트가 같으면 0, 하나라도 다르면 1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>ㅣ</td>\n<td>or</td>\n<td>모든 비트 중 한 비트라도 1이면 1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>~</td>\n<td>not</td>\n<td>각 비트의 부정 0이면 1, 1이면 0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&#x3C;&#x3C;</td>\n<td>왼쪽 시프트</td>\n<td>비트를 왼쪽으로 이동</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>>></td>\n<td>오른쪽 시프트</td>\n<td>비트를 오른쪽으로 이동</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"논리-연산자\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%85%BC%EB%A6%AC-%EC%97%B0%EC%82%B0%EC%9E%90\" aria-label=\"논리 연산자 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\